These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
House: colonial, palace, gothic-revival, victorian
1. the palace house is between the gothic-revival house and the victorian house##2
2. the palace house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the colonial house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| House   | colonial | victorian | palace | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, raspberry, peach, pineapple
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating raspberry and the person eating corn##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Food   | raspberry | pineapple | corn | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, social-worker, paramedic, police-officer
1. the police-officer is on the right of the project-manager##1
2. the paramedic is between the social-worker and the police-officer##2
3. the project-manager is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Job   | project-manager | police-officer | paramedic | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
