.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, montecristo, prince, bluemaster
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is between the montecristo-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |   2    |     3     |   4    |
| Cigar   | montecristo | bluemaster | pall-mall | prince |

