2. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsmarigold##2
3. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsrose##2
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Flower   | bellflower | rose | marigold | zinnia |

